---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro'
---
<DocsLayout title="Sponsor">
  <h1>♥ Sponsor ACSlider</h1>
  <p class="lead">ACSlider is free, open source, and MIT licensed. If it saves you time or makes your projects better, consider sponsoring development.</p>

  <div class="sponsor-card">
    <h2>GitHub Sponsors</h2>
    <p>Support directly through GitHub Sponsors. Any amount helps keep the project maintained and growing.</p>
    <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/andresclua" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="sponsor-cta">
      ♥ Sponsor on GitHub
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2>What your support funds</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Ongoing maintenance and bug fixes</li>
    <li>New plugins and effects</li>
    <li>React, Vue, and Svelte wrappers</li>
    <li>Improved documentation and demos</li>
    <li>More WebGL effects and custom shader tools</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Thank you</h2>
  <p>Every sponsor, star, and issue report makes a difference. Thank you for using ACSlider.</p>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
.sponsor-card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce7f3, #ede9fe);
  border: 1px solid #e9d5ff;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
}
.sponsor-card h2 { margin-top: 0; border: none; }
.sponsor-cta {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  padding: 10px 24px;
  background: var(--brand);
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.sponsor-cta:hover { background: var(--brand-dark); text-decoration: none; }
</style>
